reviewText: DVD worked great ... Case on the other hand was pretty beat up and there was marker on the top of disk itself

Not that I am a fan of these styles of choppers, this series gives you a good idea on how things are done. This first one in particular, shows you in detail, how Jesse makes a handmade tank, not to mention how a good paint job is done.
It is shorter than the other two, but its entertaining to say the least.
